  --- Maven
  ="true"           class="octicon octicon-link">  Download                                    Packages                     If you are using MAVEN, add this entry to your POM file:              &lt;dependency&gt;     &lt;groupId&gt;org.codehaus.janino&lt;/groupId&gt;     &lt;artifactId&gt;janino&lt;/artifactId&gt;     &lt;version&gt;***&lt;/version&gt; &lt;/dependency&gt;                     org.codehaus.janino         janino<
  --- ExpressionEvaluator
